	[["meltTask", "secTasks"], "<img image='images\power.jpg' width='370' height='208'/><br/><br/>Crippling the power in the surrounding area will put a hurting on Zane's operations. Meltdown the <marker name='pwrMkr'>Ekali Solar Plant</marker> by <font color='#D22E2E'>hacking</font> into the control room's main computer and forcing the plant into a meltdown.<br/><br/><font color='#D22E2E'>Note:</font><br/>Be sure to <font color='#D22E2E'>get clear of the plant</font> before it melts down!","Meltdown Solar Plant","", getMarkerPos "pwrMkr", "created", "INTERACT"]
	
